Want to find out more?
</a>
</h3>
<div class=accordian-panel>
<div class=accordian-panel-content>
<p>
You can find out more about data protection and the rights you have by contacting the independent Information Commissioner’s
Office:
</p>
<p>
<a href="https://ico.org.uk/" aria-label="Link for Information Commissioner’s Office" target=_blank>Information Commissioner’s Office</a>
</p>
